		"Details": "The Demon was originally created by the SLDF as its standard fighting vehicle in 2716. A match for any light or medium BattleMech, the Demon had good maneuverability and was protected by ten tons of slab armor, most of it concentrated in its front. After the dissolution the Star League, the vehicle fell from production and the design became lost during the Succession Wars. Comstar would eventually reopen the Demon factory on Terra and produce it in numbers for use by the Com Guard. The vehicle would later see service with the Word of Blake's Militia after planet's capture in 3058.\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Wheeled: Fast in open ground, slow in rough terrain.\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 4/6 Hex: 120/180 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       250     30\n<b>Left</b>         150     30\n<b>Right</b>       150     30\n<b>Rear</b>        100     30\n<b>Turret</b>      150     30\n\n<b>Total</b>      800    150\n",
